# Git commits

When creating git commits in this project:

- **Never** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any `cursoragent` co-author trailer.
- **Never** set commit author or committer to `cursoragent` or `Cursor`.
- Commits must be authored only by the human repo owner unless they explicitly ask to credit someone else.
- Other humans may be added as co-authors only when the user explicitly requests it by name/email.
